WEBVTT

00:00:02.577 --> 00:00:06.604
OKAY, THIS IS TAPE NUMBER FIVE OF AN INTERVIEW WITH RITA YELGIN

00:00:06.795 --> 00:00:09.742
ON FEBRUARY TWENTY THIRD, NINETEEN NINETY SEVEN

00:00:09.985 --> 00:00:11.801
INTERVIEWER MARK DAVID

00:00:11.892 --> 00:00:12.983
IT'S

00:00:13.123 --> 00:00:14.771
IN BROOKLINE, MASS.

00:00:16.431 --> 00:00:19.277
nu, hert zikh ayn, iz shoyn fraytik.

00:00:20.245 --> 00:00:24.846
dortn hot men mir derzen, di khaverte mayne zitst mit a grobn sider

00:00:24.953 --> 00:00:26.898
UNK azoy grob

00:00:26.898 --> 00:00:28.355
zitst nor un davnt

00:00:28.362 --> 00:00:30.465
s'iz shoyn nokh der shkhite, tseshrokene

00:00:30.589 --> 00:00:33.654
dem yid- un dortn geven etlekhe mishpokhes tsuzamen.

00:00:33.947 --> 00:00:36.390
ir tate mame, un eyner a yid

00:00:36.390 --> 00:00:38.694
vos er kumt fun lebn Vasilishok

00:00:38.694 --> 00:00:40.455
hot er gehat tsvey hoyfn.

00:00:40.832 --> 00:00:42.851
ikh gedenk shoyn nit dem yid's familye.

00:00:43.330 --> 00:00:44.674
shteyt mir far di oygn

00:00:45.034 --> 00:00:46.361
tsvey hoyfn

00:00:46.738 --> 00:00:47.744
eygene.

00:00:47.869 --> 00:00:51.187
un er hot dray tekhter un a zun.

00:00:52.797 --> 00:00:54.878
un mir esn, un ikh dertseyl zey

00:00:54.878 --> 00:00:56.202
fun mayn foter

00:00:56.202 --> 00:00:59.690
hob ikh gikh dertseylt zey, mayn foter hot gehat fraynt in Vilne

00:00:59.690 --> 00:01:01.480
un dos iz zayne fraynt oykh.

00:01:01.622 --> 00:01:03.303
zayne epes oykh eygene.

00:01:03.377 --> 00:01:05.188
kh'veys nit fun vemen, fun der

00:01:05.188 --> 00:01:07.162
tsi fun der mame's tsad tsi fun dem

00:01:07.162 --> 00:01:10.605
tsi mayn foter's ⟨kuzins⟩, tsi fun der kuzine, dos veys ikh

00:01:10.605 --> 00:01:12.416
der iker, azoy hobn mir zikh derredt.

00:01:13.452 --> 00:01:14.711
hert zikh ayn

00:01:14.751 --> 00:01:17.327
nu, un, es iz ge-

00:01:18.042 --> 00:01:20.010
shoyn avekgegangen shabes

00:01:21.568 --> 00:01:25.055
ikh dertseyl zi vos dortn, vos in Grodne tut zikh

00:01:25.112 --> 00:01:28.956
un ikh bin di same ershte, durkhn kholem, tsum kholem mayn foter

00:01:28.956 --> 00:01:30.894
vos ikh bin aroysgelofn fun Grodne.

00:01:31.558 --> 00:01:34.994
zuntik in der fri, hobn mir nor opgegesn BREAKFAST

00:01:35.288 --> 00:01:36.767
kumt tsu geyn

00:01:36.857 --> 00:01:41.238
a goy, di, di. di goyim kenen araynkumen, der geto iz nit keyn fartsoymter.

00:01:41.413 --> 00:01:43.331
iz gekumen a goye

00:01:43.708 --> 00:01:47.178
mitn shlitn. s'iz nokh FEBRUARY dokh UNK shney

00:01:47.674 --> 00:01:51.093
un zi iz ar- hot zikh nokhgefregt oyf im, hot men ir arayngefirt tsu im.

00:01:51.133 --> 00:01:55.312
far der milkhome hot zi geton BUSINESS mit dem yidn. zi hot oykh a hoyf.

00:01:55.453 --> 00:01:59.463
nor der hoyf iz oyfn ander zayt grenets, lebn a shtetl Kaminke.

00:02:01.191 --> 00:02:03.727
zogt zi zi ken nemen eyn tokhter tsu ir

00:02:03.727 --> 00:02:07.665
nit haltn ir farbahaltn ergets in a keler, nor haltn fun oybn.

00:02:08.294 --> 00:02:09.448
un

00:02:09.448 --> 00:02:12.224
di shkheynim, zi voynt oyf a kolonye

00:02:12.224 --> 00:02:14.180
zi voynt nit, s'iz nit keyn dorf.

00:02:14.180 --> 00:02:17.710
s'iz opgerukt, vayt, kh'veys, efsher a may- a kilometer

00:02:17.710 --> 00:02:19.775
tsi UNK a halbe iz a khate

00:02:19.775 --> 00:02:23.032
a shtub, ot azoy o. un LAND hobn zey un feld

00:02:23.032 --> 00:02:24.607
s'iz a ESTATE azoy vi a

00:02:25.272 --> 00:02:27.679
zogt zi zi ken nemen a tokhter

00:02:28.022 --> 00:02:30.179
UNK di tekhter viln geyn ale dray

00:02:30.179 --> 00:02:31.425
un mit der mame.

00:02:31.853 --> 00:02:35.323
zi hert ⟨zey⟩, zi, zi ken dos nit ton. me ken nit nemen.

00:02:35.447 --> 00:02:38.934
zi ken eyn tokhter nemen. zi ⟨vet⟩ shoyn oyfleygn a mayse vos do iz

00:02:39.008 --> 00:02:40.639
ir farshteyt, far di shkheynim.

00:02:41.438 --> 00:02:46.309
geblibn az keyner geyt nit, zey viln nit, un ver der lebn ⟨iz geven ikh zog dokh⟩ azoy vi got in Ades

00:02:46.399 --> 00:02:48.657
az men est CHICKEN, me bakt khale

00:02:48.657 --> 00:02:51.337
UNK meyn- hobn zey gemeynt az s'vet azoy eybik zayn.

00:02:52.677 --> 00:02:57.835
UNK hobn gemeynt az di hobn zey gemakht a shkhite genumen, ober itster vet men lozn di lebn azoy vi bay undz hot men gemeynt.

00:02:57.958 --> 00:03:01.496
az s'iz driter ray- do vet men lozn lebn di yidn. m'hot zikh ayngeredt.

00:03:02.650 --> 00:03:08.316
zogt zi "a shod der ort," az ikh dar- i- ikh darf itster avekgeyn fun zey oyf morgn, montik in der fri

00:03:08.316 --> 00:03:11.646
vayle ikh ken do lang nit zayn, vayl di POLICE kumen do arayn

00:03:11.646 --> 00:03:15.356
di poylishe, un zey kenen yeder ponem, zey veln derkenen a nayem ponem

00:03:15.711 --> 00:03:17.240
vet mir dokh arestn.

00:03:17.365 --> 00:03:19.075
ikh darf itster avekgeyn

00:03:19.075 --> 00:03:20.103
oyf Lide

00:03:20.103 --> 00:03:21.706
geyen tsum Lider geto.

00:03:21.706 --> 00:03:23.428
ot dortn zikh dervisn

00:03:23.428 --> 00:03:24.884
avu iz MEZHANTSY

00:03:25.043 --> 00:03:28.631
geyn in dem dorf, do lebn yidn geratevete fun di shkhite.

00:03:30.038 --> 00:03:35.702
zogt zi zi ken nemen eyn, eyn tokhter, iz geblibn az keyner geyt nit. zi vil nit geyn.

00:03:35.927 --> 00:03:37.558
zogt zi "a shod dem ort."

00:03:38.053 --> 00:03:42.991
zogt zi zol ikh geyn. ikh hob alts eyns nit avu tsu geyn. ikh darf geyn gor morgn oyfn Lider geto.

00:03:43.521 --> 00:03:48.226
⟨zikh arayn glay-⟩ s'iz dokh a gefar, zikh araynganvenen in shtot UNK daytshn

00:03:48.226 --> 00:03:51.120
un eyder me ganvet zikh arayn in geto, s'iz nit azoy gring.

00:03:51.120 --> 00:03:53.524
fun toyer ken ikh nit araynet, UNK daytshn hitn

00:03:53.524 --> 00:03:55.040
darf ikh dokh fun di drotn

00:03:55.114 --> 00:03:57.150
s'iz a moyre. s'iz a gefar.

00:03:58.472 --> 00:04:00.979
zogt, ot zogt er "ikh vel ir zogn, der goye

00:04:00.979 --> 00:04:03.339
az ikh bin zayne a shvester's a tokhter

00:04:03.602 --> 00:04:06.603
un zol zi mir gut haltn, un er iz zeyer a raykher yid

00:04:06.603 --> 00:04:08.273
hot er ir ongegegbn zakhn

00:04:08.273 --> 00:04:09.823
un nokh der milkhome

00:04:09.913 --> 00:04:11.797
vet er ir batsoln nokh.

00:04:12.090 --> 00:04:15.644
un zi zol in a vokh arum brengen a brivl fun mir."

00:04:15.904 --> 00:04:17.011
farshteyt?

00:04:18.317 --> 00:04:20.225
az, opgeredt azoy o.

00:04:20.225 --> 00:04:22.175
hot er ir gegebn dos vos ikh hob gezen

00:04:22.175 --> 00:04:24.275
leder, a sakh leder

00:04:24.325 --> 00:04:25.787
manufaktur

00:04:26.755 --> 00:04:29.010
f- shepsn di felkhelekh fun a sheps

00:04:29.010 --> 00:04:32.860
makhn a, a futerl far mir oyfneyen. ikh hob gehat a ⟨vinterdike⟩ mantl.

00:04:32.860 --> 00:04:35.740
ober ir veyst dokh, es vert opgenutst, alts

00:04:35.740 --> 00:04:37.020
er iz nokh geven gut

00:04:37.020 --> 00:04:40.470
nor er hot gegebn a sh- er hot dos gehat, UNK ikh zol gebn oyfneyen

00:04:40.470 --> 00:04:42.460
dortn tsu a goyishn shnayder

00:04:42.460 --> 00:04:45.410
makhn a pel- mit dem pelts hob ikh gekumen take in vald.

00:04:45.807 --> 00:04:49.347
un er hot ir gegebn a geshpan vos alts far a ferd vos me nitst

00:04:49.347 --> 00:04:51.288
vos me tut im on, ir veyst dokh az me

00:04:51.288 --> 00:04:53.271
⟨vos tsum⟩ aynshpanen a vogn.

00:04:53.271 --> 00:04:54.407
⟨dos oykh⟩ gelt.

00:04:55.020 --> 00:04:57.224
un gelt gedenk ikh nit tsi gelt oykh.

00:04:57.332 --> 00:04:59.368
nor zakhn hot er gegebn a sakh

00:05:00.589 --> 00:05:02.324
⟨iz⟩ di goye ken dokh im

00:05:02.324 --> 00:05:05.274
un zi hot dokh mit im geton BUSINESS, veyst zi er iz a erlekher man.

00:05:05.787 --> 00:05:07.723
hot zi mir genumen. itster

00:05:07.723 --> 00:05:10.223
darfn mir ganvenen dem grenets oyf tsurik, vayl zi iz

00:05:10.223 --> 00:05:11.863
punkt oyfn ander zayt grenets

00:05:11.863 --> 00:05:13.993
un Kamenke iz oyf dem zayt grenets.

00:05:15.996 --> 00:05:17.410
oyf, mir geyen

00:05:17.410 --> 00:05:21.525
zogt zi, zi, zi STOPt itster bay, oy- lebn grenets epes iz

00:05:21.801 --> 00:05:24.599
oyfn ander zayt, oyfn ander zayt, oyf di

00:05:24.599 --> 00:05:26.396
oyfn dritn raykh, avu di day-

00:05:26.396 --> 00:05:28.646
iz, iz irer a bruder.

00:05:28.855 --> 00:05:30.666
veln mir arayngeyn bay im STOPn

00:05:30.666 --> 00:05:32.460
un mir veln do ibershlofn

00:05:32.466 --> 00:05:34.336
un in der fri forn mir in

00:05:34.336 --> 00:05:36.160
vayl s'iz shoyn farmakht zuntik.

00:05:36.160 --> 00:05:37.820
forn mir in

00:05:37.820 --> 00:05:40.351
in, tsu ir in khate.

00:05:40.351 --> 00:05:42.163
tsu ir in ir ESTATE.

00:05:42.085 --> 00:05:44.981
vu iz der yingl in der tsayt? vu iz der yingl?

00:05:43.283 --> 00:05:47.024
ha? der yingl iz geblibn bay an ander FAMILY. ikh veys nit vos mit im

00:05:47.024 --> 00:05:49.084
kh'vel aykh bald dertseyln shpeter vos ikh hob zikh dervust.

00:05:49.084 --> 00:05:50.694
ober itster veys ikh gornit.

00:05:50.694 --> 00:05:53.081
er iz mit a ander FAMILY, ikh bay andere.

00:05:52.277 --> 00:05:53.823
OKAY, vayter.

00:05:53.728 --> 00:05:54.684
gey ikh

00:05:54.690 --> 00:05:56.641
mit der froy tsu ir bruder.

00:05:56.749 --> 00:05:58.071
zi hot mir gezogt

00:05:58.071 --> 00:05:59.995
az ikh nem a shtikl broyt

00:05:59.995 --> 00:06:01.688
zol ikh zikh ibertseylemen.

00:06:01.947 --> 00:06:03.901
un, un poylish reyd ikh gut

00:06:03.901 --> 00:06:06.867
un ikh bin a shikse. un zi hot oyfgeleygt a mayse

00:06:07.110 --> 00:06:09.891
az mayne a- fun vanet hot zi mir genumen?

00:06:09.891 --> 00:06:12.757
zi hot dem bruder nit dertseylt az ikh bin a yidishe. neyn.

00:06:13.168 --> 00:06:17.195
mayne el- mayn foter iz geven a ofitser, a poylisher ofitser.

00:06:18.180 --> 00:06:21.464
hot men gekumen di polyakn aroysfirn

00:06:22.095 --> 00:06:24.041
z- neyn, nit di polyakn, oy.

00:06:24.041 --> 00:06:24.986
di rusn

00:06:24.986 --> 00:06:27.269
hobn gekumen zey aroysfirn in Sibir

00:06:27.327 --> 00:06:30.173
a poylisher ofitser iz dokh a zeyerer a soyne

00:06:30.398 --> 00:06:33.058
un mir hot rikhtik a bakante fun mayn muter

00:06:33.058 --> 00:06:35.148
genumen tsu zikh un mir farbahaltn

00:06:35.148 --> 00:06:37.478
ot azoy hob ikh zikh geratevet. mayne

00:06:37.478 --> 00:06:39.468
tate mame zaynen in Sibir.

00:06:40.675 --> 00:06:43.318
dos hot zey gezo- iz dokh a mitsve rateven aza

00:06:43.476 --> 00:06:45.748
un a, un zi hot mir ongeton a tseylem

00:06:45.771 --> 00:06:47.364
trog ikh shoyn oyfn haldz

00:06:47.364 --> 00:06:48.824
un me git a shtikl broyt

00:06:48.824 --> 00:06:50.204
tseylem ikh zikh iber.

00:06:51.593 --> 00:06:53.190
un ikh nem dan a bis.

00:06:53.517 --> 00:06:54.230
nu

00:06:54.230 --> 00:06:55.920
iz

00:06:55.920 --> 00:06:59.720
un ikh murml mit di ts- mit di lipn, azoy vi ikh zog dos shtilerheyt

00:06:59.720 --> 00:07:00.900
dem PRAYER

00:07:00.900 --> 00:07:02.032
vos me darf zogn.

00:07:02.629 --> 00:07:04.918
makh ikh zikh azoy shtilerheyt mit di lipn.

00:07:05.059 --> 00:07:06.099
baveg ikh.

00:07:06.308 --> 00:07:07.601
itster

00:07:08.265 --> 00:07:09.811
hot

00:07:10.155 --> 00:07:13.051
hob ikh ibergeshlofn di nakht. m'hot undz gegebn esn

00:07:13.142 --> 00:07:16.713
dortn, un s'iz raykhe mentshn ze ikh v- nokhn esn

00:07:16.872 --> 00:07:21.422
un in der fri tsurik genumen dem ferd un mir UNK forn itster tsu ir.

00:07:21.546 --> 00:07:26.265
⟨bin gekumen⟩ tsu ir. oy, ir man iz geven a tsadik, a guter, a tayerer mentsh.

00:07:26.659 --> 00:07:28.425
un zi hot dray zin

00:07:31.148 --> 00:07:32.137
fir zin.

00:07:32.228 --> 00:07:34.401
eyner iz a khasene gehater, ⟨JURZY⟩

00:07:34.401 --> 00:07:37.110
un er voynt a, ikh veys, a fertl mayl fun ir

00:07:37.110 --> 00:07:39.360
mit a vayb un tsvey kleyne kinderlekh

00:07:39.855 --> 00:07:42.903
⟨JURZY⟩. er veys az ikh bin a, iz d- er iz gekumen

00:07:42.903 --> 00:07:44.183
hot zi im dertseylt

00:07:44.183 --> 00:07:46.743
di vayb tor nit visn. di vayb iz a antisemitke.

00:07:47.702 --> 00:07:49.563
un nokh eyn zun, MIECZUSZ

00:07:49.563 --> 00:07:51.513
⟨JURZYK⟩, MIECZUSZ, STASIEK

00:07:51.513 --> 00:07:53.720
der yingster gedenk ikh shoyn nit vi er heyst.

00:07:53.895 --> 00:07:56.639
der yingster iz mistome geven a yor zekhtsn zibetsn

00:07:58.485 --> 00:08:00.453
oyf morgn hot men gekoylet a khazer

00:08:00.763 --> 00:08:02.275
⟨alts az⟩ ikh bin gekumen

00:08:02.586 --> 00:08:05.898
un ir veyst dokh az me koylet a khazer UNK koylet a ku.

00:08:05.898 --> 00:08:07.844
iz fleysh zaltst men ayn

00:08:07.665 --> 00:08:09.633
me harget, me, me

00:08:07.868 --> 00:08:08.419
vo-

00:08:09.471 --> 00:08:12.750
zey shnaydn im iber tsi zey shtekhn im. ikh veys nit. ikh hob dos nit gezen.

00:08:12.750 --> 00:08:14.243
in a shtal tuen zey dos.

00:08:14.243 --> 00:08:17.345
ober ⟨men heybt on⟩ aropshlepn di fel, az s'iz do vos tsu esn.

00:08:17.706 --> 00:08:19.806
un me hot opgegokht kartofl

00:08:19.806 --> 00:08:22.546
mit a sakh gribenes, mit di ⟨farfetste shoyn⟩

00:08:22.546 --> 00:08:24.656
kh'hob dos ayngevoynt. fun onfang iz mir geven

00:08:24.656 --> 00:08:27.846
shver. ikh hob tsu zikh geredt, farmakht di oygn. ikh fleg reydn

00:08:27.846 --> 00:08:30.306
"dos iz gendzene shmalts. dos iz nit keyn khazer.

00:08:30.306 --> 00:08:33.090
es oyb du vilst lebn." dos fleg ikh redn tsu zikh

00:08:33.214 --> 00:08:35.182
un ikh hob gegesn. ikh hob zikh ayngevoynt

00:08:35.239 --> 00:08:36.409
mit broyt

00:08:36.409 --> 00:08:40.582
un m'hot geshtopt vursht. me hot oysgevashn di kishke. UNK vos do tut zikh

00:08:41.533 --> 00:08:43.994
un eyer hot ir gekent esn vifl ir vil.

00:08:43.994 --> 00:08:45.831
hiner UNK a raykher goy.

00:08:45.938 --> 00:08:47.732
er iz geven der soltis fun

00:08:47.732 --> 00:08:49.172
der MAYOR fun dorf.

00:08:49.583 --> 00:08:52.385
zayn hoyz iz a, in a zayt, a kolonye.

00:08:52.385 --> 00:08:55.715
ober s'iz geven vayt dortn a dorf. er iz der soltis.

00:08:55.894 --> 00:08:57.322
hot er zikh gehat gut.

00:08:58.020 --> 00:09:00.240
in di d- er hot ⟨fartseylt⟩ baym tish

00:09:00.240 --> 00:09:03.240
vi daytshn zogn im "du nem far zikh mer, nem."

00:09:03.437 --> 00:09:04.933
s'iz, zey hobn im gelernt

00:09:05.007 --> 00:09:07.532
nemen tsuker, veyst dokh, hobn mer.

00:09:08.010 --> 00:09:10.214
hert zikh ayn, iz

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:12.982
dortn bin ikh geven akht vokhn.

00:09:14.187 --> 00:09:18.540
eyn mol, ikh fleg oft geyn tsu, der zun flegt makhn branfn.

00:09:18.540 --> 00:09:19.640
un zey oykhet

00:09:19.772 --> 00:09:22.106
der goy, der, di goye's man

00:09:22.106 --> 00:09:24.221
fargesn di familye, gedenk nit.

00:09:24.244 --> 00:09:26.752
der dorf hot geheysn GLEBOVTSY.

00:09:26.893 --> 00:09:28.726
ikh gedenk nit zayn nomen.

00:09:29.003 --> 00:09:30.819
⟨vi a⟩ guter goy a tayerer.

00:09:31.078 --> 00:09:32.726
un er hot zey ge-

00:09:32.833 --> 00:09:37.116
hot er ge- gemakht branfn. ober er firt dos nit in Grodne.

00:09:37.116 --> 00:09:39.255
der zun JURZYK, der khasene gehater

00:09:39.255 --> 00:09:42.045
un di branfn flegn zey ongisn in CANen fun milkh.

00:09:42.045 --> 00:09:45.182
gute oysgevashene UNK zey hobn gehaltn SPECIAL oyf branfn.

00:09:45.182 --> 00:09:48.051
un er flegt zey araynshteln in fur, ikh veys, zeks

00:09:48.051 --> 00:09:48.853
tsi akht

00:09:48.853 --> 00:09:50.819
ts- CANen mit branfn, vifl s'iz arayn

00:09:50.819 --> 00:09:52.402
un er firt dos bay nakht

00:09:52.695 --> 00:09:55.923
un er brengt dos tsu zaynem a bakantn in Grodne

00:09:55.923 --> 00:09:58.072
un er koyft dos op bay im

00:09:58.298 --> 00:10:02.106
un yener farkoyft dos nakher kleyne bislekh vos gekumen mit flesher

00:10:02.348 --> 00:10:04.058
un nemt, me tsolt UNK gelt

00:10:04.058 --> 00:10:05.261
un zey makhn gelt.

00:10:05.318 --> 00:10:07.188
ve- yener goy fardint nokh.

00:10:07.188 --> 00:10:10.762
er farkoyft oyf biliker, un er nemt, veyst ir dokh vi es geyt handlen.

00:10:11.747 --> 00:10:13.901
eyn mol, dos iz shoyn geven

00:10:16.253 --> 00:10:17.431
MARCH

00:10:17.431 --> 00:10:20.617
iz peysekh zeyerer, zeyer EASTER.

00:10:21.805 --> 00:10:26.653
JURZYK iz avekgeforn in Daytshla- in Grodne farkoyfn branfn

00:10:26.653 --> 00:10:28.366
iz zi moy- hot moyre

00:10:28.366 --> 00:10:32.570
flegt zi m- ikh hob zikh oysgelebt mit der meydele, iz zi geven dray yor alt, DANUSIA

00:10:32.570 --> 00:10:34.356
UNK ir nomen gedenk ikh.

00:10:34.356 --> 00:10:36.247
fleg ikh ir dertseyln mayselekh

00:10:36.247 --> 00:10:38.609
zikh shpiln mit ir, hot zi mir zeyer lib gehat

00:10:38.609 --> 00:10:41.188
flegt zi mir oft betn ikh zol kumen shlofn tsu ir

00:10:42.105 --> 00:10:43.263
fleg ikh geyn

00:10:43.405 --> 00:10:45.302
o- ikh hob geshlofn dortn

00:10:45.302 --> 00:10:47.072
bay der goye in ir BEDROOM

00:10:47.072 --> 00:10:48.342
oyf a hiltserne bank

00:10:48.342 --> 00:10:51.452
vos zikh epes funandergeleygt, iz dos geven azoy vi a betl.

00:10:52.467 --> 00:10:55.735
un di kin- di zin hobn geshlofn in an ander tsimer.

00:10:56.078 --> 00:10:58.991
di vos, un der khasene gehater hot gevoynt mit der vayb.

00:10:59.200 --> 00:11:01.584
shlof ikh bay ir in d- in LIVING ROOM

00:11:01.584 --> 00:11:02.721
oyf a COUCH.

00:11:03.199 --> 00:11:05.505
eyn mol in der fri, dos iz geven MARCH

00:11:06.355 --> 00:11:07.395
shteyt zi.

00:11:07.738 --> 00:11:09.554
i- vekt zi mir oyf.

00:11:09.730 --> 00:11:11.192
ikh khap zikh oyf.

00:11:11.637 --> 00:11:14.938
ikh ze zi shteyt lebn mayn COUCH oyf di kni UNK

00:11:15.484 --> 00:11:17.705
mir hot men gerufn dortn STASZKA

00:11:18.117 --> 00:11:21.418
"STASZKA" makht, a toyte, a tseshrokene.

00:11:21.525 --> 00:11:23.184
"mir hot zikh itster gekholemt.

00:11:23.184 --> 00:11:25.333
yidn hobn mir gekumen nemen oyf matse."

00:11:25.423 --> 00:11:27.890
vayl azoy iz arumgegangen zabubones UNK

00:11:27.890 --> 00:11:31.250
az yidn kenen nit bakn di matses. zey muzn araynton goyishn blut.

00:11:31.250 --> 00:11:32.119
veyst ir dos?

00:11:32.119 --> 00:11:33.072
dos hobn a mol

00:11:33.072 --> 00:11:34.529
farshpreyt galokhim

00:11:34.705 --> 00:11:36.352
gor a mol nokh in Poyln.

00:11:36.443 --> 00:11:39.940
nu, iz zi iz zeyer a frume, di, di shnur, di shviger ire

00:11:39.940 --> 00:11:42.270
hot mir dertseylt az di shnur iz zeyer a frume.

00:11:42.771 --> 00:11:44.137
iz zi gleybt dos.

00:11:44.137 --> 00:11:46.347
az zey tuen dos nokh haynt, azoy andersh ken nit di ma-

00:11:46.347 --> 00:11:48.417
un bald vet dokh zayn der yidisher peysekh.

00:11:48.660 --> 00:11:49.830
darfn zey hobn

00:11:49.830 --> 00:11:53.818
a, a, emetsn koylenen, zey darfn dokh di goyishe blut oyf matse bakn.

00:11:54.432 --> 00:11:57.041
hot ir dos ir gekholemt az me vet kumen ir nemen.

00:11:57.132 --> 00:12:00.113
shteyt zi un zi treyslt zikh. ikh glet ir

00:12:00.203 --> 00:12:03.634
un ikh trakht bay mir in kop tsi hot zi oyfgemakht di mayse

00:12:03.634 --> 00:12:05.692
un zi hot derkent az ikh bin a yidishe

00:12:05.692 --> 00:12:07.992
tsi zi hot oyf emes gehat aza kholem

00:12:08.050 --> 00:12:09.158
vos iz dos?

00:12:09.332 --> 00:12:13.513
aleyn bin ikh a tseshrokene fun ir, vayl zi shteyt UNK mir oyfgevekt itster fun shlof

00:12:13.513 --> 00:12:14.779
s'iz nokh azoy

00:12:14.779 --> 00:12:16.735
o- nor genumen vern tog

00:12:18.175 --> 00:12:20.447
kler ikh ikh darf shoyn fun danen oykh avekgeyn.

00:12:20.638 --> 00:12:24.311
nor vi geyt men az ikh bin azoy vayt? ikh bin gor itster tsurik in dritn raykh.

00:12:25.802 --> 00:12:26.994
meyle

00:12:27.709 --> 00:12:29.728
nu, ot azoy hob ikh ⟨zikh⟩ baruikt

00:12:29.852 --> 00:12:33.828
un mir zaynen gegangen esn BREAKFAST, un der man iz gekumen fun Grodne

00:12:34.138 --> 00:12:36.430
un zi ⟨hot mistome tsu⟩ im dertseylt. ikh hob nit gehert

00:12:36.430 --> 00:12:38.420
un ikh bin shoyn avek tsurik tsu mayn goye.

00:12:38.420 --> 00:12:40.579
tsu di, tsu i- tsu dayn tate mame.

00:12:40.973 --> 00:12:43.414
un ikh hob gornit dertseylt mit ir kholem, gornit.

00:12:43.538 --> 00:12:45.726
nor ikh ho- ikh aleyn bin ikh geven tseshrokn.

00:12:45.816 --> 00:12:47.447
UNK oykh nit geven zikher

00:12:49.022 --> 00:12:51.513
es fleg kumen i- oft flegn kumen daytshn

00:12:51.604 --> 00:12:54.064
ven ikh, durkhn fentster hot men zey gekent zen

00:12:54.064 --> 00:12:57.372
mitn veg, aza shmole veg firt tsu zeyer hoyf

00:12:57.372 --> 00:13:01.641
vi es kumen daytshn. zey darfn a podkeve, epes fun di ferd

00:13:01.641 --> 00:13:02.603
farrikhtn

00:13:02.603 --> 00:13:04.541
un zayne zin hobn dos gekent.

00:13:05.121 --> 00:13:09.893
flegt men mir glaykh aroyfshikn mi- mit a leyter in der heykh. dortn hobn di hiner zikh geleygt

00:13:09.893 --> 00:13:11.033
di eyer.

00:13:11.033 --> 00:13:13.978
fleg ikh glaykh aroyfgeyn dortn, me zol mir nit zen.

00:13:13.978 --> 00:13:15.498
darf men zikh farentfern

00:13:15.498 --> 00:13:17.234
far di goyim, far di shkheynim

00:13:17.234 --> 00:13:21.031
hot zi shoyn gehat di mayse, UNK mayne eltern zaynen ofitser geven.

00:13:21.031 --> 00:13:24.566
m'hot farshikt in Sibir. UNK zey hobn in gantsn nit gevolt reydn

00:13:24.566 --> 00:13:27.490
hot mir aroyf⟨UNK⟩ UNK zikh farbahaltn, az ikh hob gezen

00:13:27.490 --> 00:13:30.410
durkh a lokh fun boydem az zey geyen shoyn avek

00:13:30.410 --> 00:13:32.688
fleg ikh dan pamelekh aropgeyn fun, mitn leyter.

00:13:34.264 --> 00:13:35.473
itster

00:13:37.032 --> 00:13:37.920
ma-

00:13:38.449 --> 00:13:40.299
makht zikh eyn mol

00:13:40.778 --> 00:13:42.392
kholemt zikh mir di mame.

00:13:42.533 --> 00:13:43.826
vayter a kholem.

00:13:44.625 --> 00:13:46.239
zogt zi mir "⟨demol⟩"

00:13:46.819 --> 00:13:51.249
i- nit ⟨demol⟩ "do darfstu mer nit zayn. du darfst avekgeyn fun danen.

00:13:51.249 --> 00:13:52.999
un gey avu der pape hot shoyn gezogt.

00:13:52.999 --> 00:13:55.559
⟨avu Tevke⟩ hot gezogt, lebn dortn yidn

00:13:55.559 --> 00:13:59.039
arum Radn in, dortn, MEZHANTSY, ot in der PUSZCZA in der

00:13:59.039 --> 00:14:01.410
in di velder lebn yidn geratevete

00:14:01.410 --> 00:14:03.333
fun di shkhites

00:14:03.373 --> 00:14:06.506
fun di AUSSIEDLUNGEN vos m'hot aroysgeshikt yidn."

00:14:07.288 --> 00:14:09.897
⟨nor⟩ vi geyt men? vi ken ikh aleyn zey trefn?

00:14:10.849 --> 00:14:13.832
makht zikh rikhtik epes in a vokh arum UNK

00:14:13.832 --> 00:14:17.536
kumt tsu geyn ire a tokhter vos zi voynt gor lebn VASILISHOK. s'iz vayt

00:14:17.536 --> 00:14:19.365
un s'iz oyf yenem zayt grenets.

00:14:20.215 --> 00:14:22.152
kumt zi zen der mamen

00:14:22.152 --> 00:14:24.731
un zi kumt betn epes bay der mamen

00:14:24.838 --> 00:14:27.965
un di mame git ir, ikh gedenk shoyn nit vos zi hot ir gegebn

00:14:27.965 --> 00:14:28.944
keyn sakh

00:14:28.944 --> 00:14:30.367
shlepn kenen zey dokh nit.

00:14:30.610 --> 00:14:33.321
hot ir gegebn gelt, ikh veys nit vos zi hot ⟨nokh⟩ gegebn.

00:14:34.153 --> 00:14:37.961
vos zi hot ⟨nokh⟩ gegebn gedenk ikh nit. un

00:14:39.402 --> 00:14:42.180
s'tra- falt mir arayn a gedank, ikh vel gor mit ir avek.

00:14:42.388 --> 00:14:44.207
zi iz dokh alts nenter dortn

00:14:44.207 --> 00:14:46.617
Vasilishok iz dokh nenter tsu MEZHANTSY.

00:14:47.586 --> 00:14:50.482
zogt di mame az zi vet undz avekfirn

00:14:50.742 --> 00:14:52.238
biz ir bruder.

00:14:52.345 --> 00:14:54.822
iz epes a fuftsn kilometer fun ir khate.

00:14:54.822 --> 00:14:56.847
un dos iz shoyn noent lebn grenets.

00:14:56.847 --> 00:15:00.388
dortn darfn mir ibershlofn di nakht, un in der fri

00:15:00.681 --> 00:15:03.459
ibergeyn dem grenets un WALKen.

00:15:04.005 --> 00:15:05.669
un mir zaynen in groys shrek.

00:15:06.148 --> 00:15:09.365
UNK. UNK ken nokh trefn daytshn

00:15:10.958 --> 00:15:12.364
nu, for ikh mit zey.

00:15:12.364 --> 00:15:15.643
UNK di mame geyt shoyn avekgeyn fun danen. do shoyn mer ken ikh nit zayn.

00:15:17.573 --> 00:15:23.712
f- gey ikh avek mit ir, mit der goye, un zi, zi hot ongezogt der tokhter

00:15:23.712 --> 00:15:25.447
az, az mir, az

00:15:25.673 --> 00:15:28.504
sh- ven zi vet zikh mit mir zegenen

00:15:28.504 --> 00:15:30.234
zol zi tsunemen dem tseylem.

00:15:30.145 --> 00:15:31.202
mh

00:15:30.234 --> 00:15:32.057
zi hot oykh gegleybt in JESUSn.

00:15:32.057 --> 00:15:35.187
az dos iz UNK ton an aveyre vos zi hot dos gegebn a yidishe.

00:15:35.187 --> 00:15:37.969
oyf, oyf avekgebn, oyf, FOR GOOD, ir veyst dokh.

00:15:38.548 --> 00:15:40.887
iz o- trog ikh nokh dem tseylem. nu?

00:15:41.198 --> 00:15:42.722
kumen mir

00:15:43.186 --> 00:15:44.785
lebn

00:15:45.771 --> 00:15:48.612
tsum, tsum bruder, dos iz azoy

00:15:48.612 --> 00:15:50.782
zi voynt do lebn Kamenke

00:15:50.782 --> 00:15:53.552
un dos alts driter raykh, un do iz der grenets

00:15:53.719 --> 00:15:55.299
un der bruder voynt do.

00:15:55.390 --> 00:15:57.358
fuftsn kilometer iz dos geven.

00:15:57.415 --> 00:15:58.618
kumen mir tsu im

00:15:58.618 --> 00:16:00.364
di goye hot oykh zikh gezetsn

00:16:00.364 --> 00:16:04.616
un fartog iz zi avekgeforn mitn fur dortn, un mir klaybn zikh, itster geyen mir

00:16:04.616 --> 00:16:06.136
⟨vi oyf⟩ tsuWALKen a bisl

00:16:06.136 --> 00:16:08.647
tsum grenets un ganvenen dem grenets.

00:16:09.278 --> 00:16:10.419
meyle

00:16:10.847 --> 00:16:12.444
mir geyen tseshrokene

00:16:13.564 --> 00:16:14.587
un

00:16:15.285 --> 00:16:17.776
azoy vi mir geyen iber dem grenets

00:16:18.222 --> 00:16:20.595
kumt antkegn a alter goy

00:16:20.753 --> 00:16:22.029
nit keyn hoykher

00:16:23.503 --> 00:16:26.501
oyf a shtikl BRANCH halt er a pekl

00:16:26.642 --> 00:16:29.313
oyf a BRANCH fun a, a tsvayg fun a

00:16:28.093 --> 00:16:29.403
a, a tsvayg

00:16:29.313 --> 00:16:31.428
fun a boym halt er a pekl

00:16:31.553 --> 00:16:33.403
mit a bord a kleyne

00:16:33.662 --> 00:16:34.620
un er zogt

00:16:34.620 --> 00:16:38.518
"CICHO NA GRANICY. shtil oyfn grenets

00:16:38.518 --> 00:16:40.864
ir hot zikh gornit vos moyre tsu hobn."

00:16:40.864 --> 00:16:42.830
mir hern di feyglen tsvitshern

00:16:42.830 --> 00:16:44.911
di feyglen, dos iz dokh shoyn APRIL.

00:16:45.475 --> 00:16:47.123
es iz shoyn gevorn APRIL.

00:16:46.150 --> 00:16:48.591
vos hor er gezogt? ikh hob nisht gehert.

00:16:47.500 --> 00:16:50.599
di feyglen tsvi- oyf daytsh iz dos tsvitshern.

00:16:49.491 --> 00:16:51.729
un vos hot der alter man gezogt?

00:16:51.904 --> 00:16:54.550
"CICHO NA GRANICY." s'iz oyf poylish.

00:16:54.550 --> 00:16:58.142
"shtil iz oyfn grenets. ir hot zikh gornit vos moyre hobn."

00:16:58.722 --> 00:17:01.584
oyf hayntikn tog zog ikh az dos iz geven a malekh.

00:17:02.451 --> 00:17:04.385
mir hobn zikh beyde bald baruikt

00:17:04.542 --> 00:17:06.750
un mir geyen, ven se geyen on daytshn

00:17:06.750 --> 00:17:08.801
zogt zi dokh az ikh bin a yidishe

00:17:08.801 --> 00:17:12.329
un fun vanen kenst ir? volt zi dokh gezogt az ⟨ikh hob ir⟩ getrofn ot o do

00:17:12.329 --> 00:17:15.399
un ikh volt dos nit opgeleyknt. UNK ⟨derfun⟩ ikh'l zogn

00:17:15.399 --> 00:17:18.139
ikh bin geven bay ir mame. vos ken dos mir helfn?

00:17:18.194 --> 00:17:20.365
UNK vet araynshlepn ir in a blote.

00:17:20.693 --> 00:17:23.314
ikh veys vos er ge⟨UNK⟩, me volt mir geshosn

00:17:23.314 --> 00:17:24.399
un zi volt avek.

00:17:24.792 --> 00:17:27.250
i- ikh gleyb UNK dos iz geven a malekh.

00:17:27.527 --> 00:17:29.208
mayn muter volt zikher gezogt.

00:17:29.265 --> 00:17:31.773
mayn muter iz geven a frume, un dos iz geven a malekh.

00:17:32.083 --> 00:17:33.865
geyen mir, WALKen mir

00:17:33.889 --> 00:17:36.481
zaynen mir shoyn lebn ir khate, lebn ir shtub

00:17:36.505 --> 00:17:38.889
hot zi mir gebrakht in a veldl

00:17:38.889 --> 00:17:41.005
nit a, a kleyner vald

00:17:41.010 --> 00:17:43.977
un zi hot mir do avekgeleygt. zi hot ongeshlept BRANCHES

00:17:43.977 --> 00:17:45.268
un farshteln zikh

00:17:45.268 --> 00:17:49.681
un zi hot ⟨azoy gezogt⟩ "do vest zayn, un ikh ⟨volt⟩ ir kumen eyn mol a tog ⟨volt⟩ ir brengen esn

00:17:49.681 --> 00:17:52.074
un ikh vel dir zogn ven du kenst geyn vayter."

00:17:52.300 --> 00:17:54.504
tsen teg hob ikh do in veldl geven.

00:17:54.561 --> 00:17:55.545
tsen teg.

00:17:55.545 --> 00:17:57.002
un zi hot mir gebrakht

00:17:57.193 --> 00:18:02.097
a, nokh farnakht. ir man tor gornit visn. ir man iz a groyser antisemit un hot faynt yidn.

00:18:02.948 --> 00:18:04.328
hot zi mir gebrakht

00:18:04.328 --> 00:18:06.637
a krug mit vareme zup

00:18:06.643 --> 00:18:07.936
mit broyt

00:18:08.061 --> 00:18:10.637
un a krigl a kleynem mit milkh

00:18:10.947 --> 00:18:12.004
vareme.

00:18:12.617 --> 00:18:14.855
zog ikh aykh ikh hob gemeynt az bin in ganeydn

00:18:15.807 --> 00:18:17.643
nu, un ikh hob gegesn. ikh zits

00:18:17.643 --> 00:18:20.933
un trinken az me hot zikh gevolt iz hob ikh gefunen a stav

00:18:20.933 --> 00:18:22.044
aza

00:18:22.337 --> 00:18:23.900
a luzhe fun

00:18:24.075 --> 00:18:27.849
hob ikh dortn gegangen. ikh hob gehat a tikhl, aza shtikl tikhl fun

00:18:27.906 --> 00:18:29.368
fun

00:18:29.695 --> 00:18:33.429
vi ruft men dos? ikh hob gehat ⟨dem vaser⟩ nemen, dem krigl fun di milkh fleg ikh ⟨onnemen⟩

00:18:33.429 --> 00:18:35.933
vaser un dos durkhzayn durkh der shtikl

00:18:38.166 --> 00:18:40.289
vi ruft men di, IRISHe

00:18:40.289 --> 00:18:44.201
IRISH LINEN a shtikl. dos zol, un dos hob ikh getrunken, di vaser

00:18:44.545 --> 00:18:45.889
un ikh zits do.

00:18:46.452 --> 00:18:49.922
di tsayt hob ikh zikh oysgelernt tsu farshteyn mit der levone.

00:18:50.333 --> 00:18:51.899
ot iz shoyn do in dem ovnt

00:18:51.899 --> 00:18:55.097
veys ikh do di levone iz do iz, do iz, do iz EAST.

00:18:55.097 --> 00:18:57.289
un di lev- levone vandert zikh ot azoy

00:18:57.289 --> 00:18:59.849
un zi fargeyt ot do, veys ikh az dos iz WEST.

00:18:59.867 --> 00:19:02.122
azoy hob ikh zikh oysgelernt farshteyn di tsayt

00:19:02.533 --> 00:19:03.455
dortn.

00:19:03.698 --> 00:19:06.375
nu, iz

00:19:08.912 --> 00:19:10.914
hob ikh opgeven di tsen teg

00:19:10.937 --> 00:19:15.321
dem tseyleml hot zi tsugenumen bay mir, un zi zogt haynt iz a mark tog.

00:19:15.321 --> 00:19:17.022
s'iz epes ye geven a dinstik

00:19:17.198 --> 00:19:20.348
un du kenst ruik geyn tsu dayn dorf, MEZHANTSY

00:19:20.348 --> 00:19:23.148
un du vest farbaygeyn a kloyster, zolst zikh ibertseylemen.

00:19:23.148 --> 00:19:26.695
vayl UNK nito keyn yidn. UNK a mol flegn geyn yidn oykh oyf di vegn

00:19:26.695 --> 00:19:28.296
ober haynt iz nor goyim.

00:19:28.605 --> 00:19:32.221
veys ikh, ot o gey ikh farbay, un ikh ze fun dem zayt a roytn kloyster

00:19:32.221 --> 00:19:33.915
tseylem ikh zikh glaykh iber.

00:19:34.039 --> 00:19:35.332
un ikh gey vayter.

00:19:35.997 --> 00:19:37.442
kum ikh arayn

00:19:38.595 --> 00:19:40.456
gey ikh azoy mit dem shosey

00:19:40.456 --> 00:19:42.251
kum ikh arayn tsu a

00:19:42.460 --> 00:19:43.483
a khate.

00:19:44.232 --> 00:19:46.042
geklert s'iz shoyn bald farnakht

00:19:46.042 --> 00:19:48.413
o, o, di mame, ven zi hot zikh mir gekholemt

00:19:48.413 --> 00:19:51.122
vos zi gi- zi git mir goldene COINS

00:19:51.122 --> 00:19:52.851
un zi zogt mir avekgeyn fun danen

00:19:52.851 --> 00:19:54.395
zogt zi "⟨du hob⟩ nit moyre

00:19:54.395 --> 00:19:58.395
du vest nit zayn aleyn. du vest mir nit zen, ober ikh'l WALKen mit dir. ikh'l geyn mit dir.

00:19:58.395 --> 00:19:59.531
ikh vel dir hitn."

00:19:59.993 --> 00:20:01.011
kler ikh azoy

00:20:01.011 --> 00:20:03.339
un ikh WALK azoy, kler ikh UNK

00:20:03.339 --> 00:20:05.693
ikh ze dir nit mame, ober ikh veys az du bist do oykh

